            "id": 6132492,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉創新高24570點後 殺尾盤豬羊變色跌3點 月K連4紅漲690點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (29) 日早盤一度上漲逾 330 點衝上 24570.15 點，改寫歷史盤中新高，不過，隨著獲利賣壓出籠、大盤開高走低，最後一盤更下殺 68 點翻黑，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>終場下跌 3.35 點收今日最低 24233.1 點，成交量 4646 億元。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6132492/l/b263c81974b066e4172ae597f01e972d.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股盤後〉創新高24570點後 殺尾盤豬羊變色跌3點 月K連4紅漲690點。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>本周仍上漲 468 點、漲近 2%；8 月更是上漲 690.58 點，漲幅 2.9%，月 K 線連 4 紅。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>觀察今日權值股表現，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 開高走低，收平盤 1160 元，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>)、聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 等均跌逾 1%，不過，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 力守紅盤，日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%、京元電子 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2449:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2449-TW</a>) 更以漲停作收。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高價股今日表現強勢，盤中更一度閃現 25 千金，追平台股記錄，貿聯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3665:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3665\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3665-TW</a>) 重返千元，盤中漲停鎖住改寫新天價、智邦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>) 也漲逾 3%，躋身千金行列，健測 (2095-TW) 漲停登上 2000 元大關，也改寫新天價。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>世芯 *-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3661-TW</a>) 則站穩 4000 元之上、川湖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2059:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2059\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2059-TW</a>) 漲逾 3%，收 3000 元之上、漢唐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2404:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2404\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2404-TW</a>) 也逾 3%，穎崴 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6515:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6515\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6515-TW</a>)、精測 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6510:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6510-TW</a>) 均收漲停，不過，旭隼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6409-TW</a>) 收盤跌近 2%，跌落千元之下。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>軍工股也是今日盤面焦點，漢翔 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2634:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2634\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2634-TW</a>) 爆出近 21.77 萬張大量、收漲 4%，台船 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2208:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2208\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2208-TW</a>) 也漲 3.8%、龍德造船 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6573:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6573\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6573-TW</a>) 收漲停；機器人族群今日回檔修正，慧友 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5484:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5484\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5484-TW</a>) 跌停、新漢 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8234:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8234\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8234-TW</a>) 也跌逾 3%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6132492",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 14:14:59",
